name: Hikari #3633
description: Beginning with 5,555 Souls, Hikari is a collection of ‘initiates’ created by Jeez & Chain-X.  A soul’s energy can be transferred into an initiate and raised within the Gen-U experience. The resulting art is generated based on in-game decision data.  Holders gain access to future collections, airdrops, comics, streetwear and playable characters within our MOBA: Legends of Hikari. Welcome to the home of the misfits 光

asset_contract.name: Hikari
asset_contract.description:
Soul Count: 2,620

Initiate Count: 2,935 - as of 01/06/22

Hikari Souls can be transferred into an ‘initiate’ through Gen-U, our interactive web experience.

How to claim your initiate:

 1.Find a soul and check its current Gen-U progress. Some souls will be pending reveal and others may have already partially played Gen-U: [HERE](https://status.hikarinft.com/token-status)

2.Take your soul through Gen-U. In game actions determine your clan, gender and other features: [HERE](https://play.hikarinft.com/)

3.Submit your Gen-U data before 4am EST and have it reveal within 24H!

Beginning with 5,555 Souls, Hikari is a collection of ‘initiates’ created by Jeez & ChainX.

A soul’s energy can be transferred into an initiate and raised within the Gen-U experience. The resulting art is generated based on in-game decision data.

Holders gain access to future collections, airdrops, comics, streetwear and playable characters within our MOBA: Legends of Hikari.

Welcome to the home of the misfits.
